property interface, component, handler

on construct me
  [  0] pushzero ................................ <0>
  [  1] setprop 836 ............................. interface = 0
  [  4] pushzero ................................ <0>
  [  5] setprop 837 ............................. component = 0
  [  8] pushzero ................................ <0>
  [  9] setprop 7 ............................... handler = 0
  [ 11] pushint8 1 .............................. <1>
  [ 13] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <1>
  [ 15] extcall 11 .............................. return 1
  [ 17] ret
end

on deconstruct me
  [  0] pushzero ................................ <0>
  [  1] setprop 836 ............................. interface = 0
  [  4] pushzero ................................ <0>
  [  5] setprop 837 ............................. component = 0
  [  8] pushzero ................................ <0>
  [  9] setprop 7 ............................... handler = 0
  [ 11] pushint8 1 .............................. <1>
  [ 13] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <1>
  [ 15] extcall 11 .............................. return 1
  [ 17] ret
end

on getInterface me
  [  0] getprop 836 ............................. <interface>
  [  3] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <interface>
  [  5] extcall 11 .............................. return interface
  [  7] ret
end

on getComponent me
  [  0] getprop 837 ............................. <component>
  [  3] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <component>
  [  5] extcall 11 .............................. return component
  [  7] ret
end

on getHandler me
  [  0] getprop 7 ............................... <handler>
  [  2] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <handler>
  [  4] extcall 11 .............................. return handler
  [  6] ret
end
